{"tid":2057001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八旬老翁遭控襲擊致造成身體傷害准保釋","createTime":"2020-06-09T05:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T05:45:40.000Z","uid":5737,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f04138ba52098c8b119e92fc2d09d8ee303d29","tid":2057001,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"社民連「長毛」梁國雄早前在中聯辦外請願期間，一名 81 歲老翁被指突然衝向梁國雄，以尖錐利器刺傷其右腰，被控一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，今日（9 日）在東區裁判法院提訊。案件押後至 8 月 4 日再訊，老翁准保釋，期間不得騷擾梁國雄。<br />\n<br />\n被告黃森球（81 歲，無業），被控於本年 4 月 16 日在西營盤均益大廈第三期外襲擊梁國雄，因而對梁造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n被告今日毋須答辯，案件押後至 8 月 4 日再訊，以待控方索取法律意見。被告准以現金 500 元擔保，期間須居住在報稱地址、不得騷擾梁國雄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8%E5%88%BA-%E9%95%B7%E6%AF%9B-%E5%8F%B3%E8%85%B0-%E5%85%AB%E6%97%AC%E8%80%81%E7%BF%81%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E8%87%B4%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E5%82%B7%E5%AE%B3%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%2588%25BA-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25AF%259B-%25E5%258F%25B3%25E8%2585%25B0-%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2597%25AC%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=27ced3af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%2588%25BA-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25AF%259B-%25E5%258F%25B3%25E8%2585%25B0-%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2597%25AC%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2582%25B